C orders|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2010-09-28/rajkot/28223238_1_airfield-mehsana-aaa|accessdate=23 January 2012|newspaper=[[The Times of India]]|date=28 September 2010}}</ref>\n\nThe airport was at the centre of a dispute between its owners and the Mehsana Municipality, which sealed the facility twice in 2010 due to non payment of taxes. AAA Ltd however contended that it is not liable to pay the said taxes. The facility was reopened after the [[Gujarat High Court]] ordered the same.<ref name=toi10/>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.aaa.co.in/ Ahmedabad Aviation and Aeronautics Ltd. website]\n{{Airports in India|state=autocollapse}}\n\n[[Category:Airports in Gujarat]]\n[[Category:Mehsana district]]\n[[Category:Mehsana]]\n", "name_user": "Jaywardhan009", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mehsana_Airport"}
