es=no |d=no}}\n* {{URL|http://agra.nic.in/|Official website of Agra district}}\n* {{curlie|Regional/Asia/India/Uttar_Pradesh/Districts/Agra}}\n* {{URL|http://digitalcollections.lib.washington.edu/cdm/search/collection/ic/searchterm/R%20Nath!Agra/field/creato!covera/mode/all!all/conn/and!and/order/title R. Nath Mughal Architecture Image Collection, images of Agra|University of Washington digital collections}}\n{{Portal bar|India}}\n<!--start of Navigation boxes-->\n{{Navboxes\n|list =\n{{Agra district}}\n{{Uttar Pradesh}}\n{{Agra Division topics}}\n{{Million-plus cities in India}}\n}}\n<!--end of Navigation boxes-->\n{{Tourist attractions in Agra}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Agra]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Agra district]]\n[[Category:Former capital cities in India]]\n[[Category:Populated places established in 1504]]\n[[Category:Tourism in Uttar Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Municipal corporations in Uttar Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Cities in Uttar Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Agra district]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|City in Uttar Pradesh, India}}\n{{Other uses}}\n{{Multiple issues|\n{{More citations needed|date=September 2019}}\n{{Cleanup rewrite|date=September 2019}}\n}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Agra\n| native_name                     = <!-- Please do not add any Indic script in this infobox, per WP:INDICSCRIPT policy. -->\n| settlement_type                 = [[City]]\n| image_skyline                   = {{Photomontage |border=0 |size=275 |spacing=2 |color=none |photo1a=Taj Mahal in India.jpg | photo2a = Amar Singh Gate, Agra Fort.jpg | photo3a = Itmad-ud-Daula's tomb-Agra3.jpg| photo2b = Tomb of Akbar the Great.jpg}}\n| image_alt                       = \n| image_caption                   = ''From top:'' The [[Taj Mahal]], Amar Singh Gate of the [[Agra Fort]], [[Tomb of Akbar the Great]], [[Tomb of I'tim\u0101d-ud-Daulah]].\n| nickname      